name: 30TP Bundle for [NA] Zachariel Server
description: You will receive 30TP to use in-game. You may only use this item on [NA] Zachariel server. Please note that TP can be received via TP UI button on up right side of screen, next to Minimap. Against Chargeback Fraud, Users whom have new steam accounts, or accounts with short purchase history will be applied with Monthly in-Game TP Shop Usage Limit of 1000TP. In order to lift the monthly purchase limit, please contact our Ticket System.
